addUsersToGroup
  ∷ ∀ f
  . Foldable f
  ⇒ Pt.AbsFile Pt.Sandboxed
  → f QA.UserId
  → QuasarAFCE Unit
addUsersToGroup pt us =
  modifyGroup pt { addUsers: foldMap pure us, removeUsers: [] }

removeUsersFromGroup
  ∷ ∀ f
  . Foldable f
  ⇒ Pt.AbsFile Pt.Sandboxed
  → f QA.UserId
  → QuasarAFCE Unit
removeUsersFromGroup pt us =
  modifyGroup pt { addUsers: [], removeUsers: foldMap pure us }


